#### Configuring Test

Once a new instance of Test is created, the mode can be set to correspond to the language being typed.

```javascript
AUI().use(
  'aui-ace-test',
  function(A) {
    new A.Test(
      {
        boundingBox: '#myTest',
        mode: 'javascript'
      }
    ).render();
  }
);
```

The test can also be set to load with content/code already written.

```javascript
AUI().use(
  'aui-test',
  function(Y) {
    new Y.Test(
      {
        boundingBox: '#myTest',
        mode: 'xml',
        value: '<body id="content"></body>'
      }
    ).render();
  }
);
```